				<h3 id="post-5518"><a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?p=5518" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Shirt, Imported">Shirt, Imported</a></h3>
				<small>Friday, January 21st, 2011</small>

				<div class="entry">
					<p>I&#8217;m thinking about buying myself <a href="http://www.rockmount.com/shirts/vintage.htm">this shirt</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p><center><img src="http://www.rockmount.com/shirts/6865/6865%20confed%20em.jpg"/></center><br />
This historical design is in honor of the trials and tribulations our nation faced and overcame. Highly detailed with special treatments it has stars on the collar, appliqued navy bars and shotgun cuffs. Piping is the final touch. Imported. </p></blockquote>
<p>What kind of soiree do you suppose it would be appropriate to wear such a shirt to?</p>
				</div>

